data.title: 17 YEARS!!! Over 21 years together and 17 years of marriage…. Still feels like yesterday and I love you more each day. Cheers to dating...
data.meta_description:
734 likes, 94 comments - jillpowellglam on September 24, 2023: "17 YEARS!!!

Over 21 years together and 17 years of marriage…. Still feels like yesterday and I love you more each day. Cheers to dating your spouse and never getting tired of each other. Thank you for supporting me and allowing me to chase my dreams and have the perfect family. Not many can do both and I am able to because of YOU. People say marriage isn’t easy- I guess I got lucky because being married to you is the easiest part of my life. Love you babe!".
